== ShareAcl v0.5 - 2026-07-01 ==

New features:
- Added SwapView page to allow swapping one trustee for another in a given scope. Target trustees are persisted in the database for future use.
- Allowed the GUI to be used without a scan selected, for live operations on the current ACLs of the system. In this mode, only the SwapView page is available.
- Added new launcher script Start-ShareAcl.ps1 as a bulletproof way to dispose of handles by running the GUI in a separate process. This is the recommended way to launch the GUI, especially when running multiple instances.

Futureproofing:
- Modified schema to store audit log entries for ACE changes, including the original ACEs and the new ACEs, to support future auditing capabilities.

Cleanup:
- Replaced built-in $args variable with a more descriptive $sqlArgs variable in Start-ShareAclGui.ps1 to avoid potential conflicts with other scripts.

Bug fixes:
- Additional crash fixes in the GUI when too many handles were open, by running additional cleanup at startup, Show-PrincipalPicker, and SwapView page unload.

== ShareAcl v0.4 - 2026-06-29 ==

New features:
- Added FindingsView page to show all findings and their associated folders and ACEs.

Bug fixes:
- Fixed crash when too many handles were open in the GUI by detaching event handlers and clearing the ItemsSource of the DataGrid when closing a page.

== ShareAcl v0.3 - 2026-06-29 ==

New features:
- Added AccountView page to show all accounts and their associated folders and ACEs.

Improvements:
- Added indexing to the database schema for efficient lookup of ACEs by trustee and folder.
- Added indexing to the database schema for efficient lookup of ACEs by rights mask and access control type.

Bug fixes:
- Fixed issue with group membership resolution in Invoke-ShareAclResolver.ps1 to include primary group members and de-duplicate results by SID.